description:
SafeReads currently only has Google OAuth. Add Password provider for email/password login to match SafeTunes and SafeTube.

## Current State
- convex/auth.ts: Only has Google provider
- No email/password login option on frontend

## Changes Needed
### Backend (convex/auth.ts)
Add Password provider with Resend for password reset:
```typescript
import { Password } from '@convex-dev/auth/providers/Password';
import { Resend } from '@auth/core/providers/resend';

export const { auth, signIn, signOut, store, isAuthenticated } = convexAuth({
  providers: [
    Password({
      id: 'password',
      reset: Resend({
        id: 'resend-otp',
        apiKey: process.env.RESEND_API_KEY,
        from: 'SafeReads <noreply@getsafereads.com>',
      }),
    }),
    Google,
  ],
});
```

### Frontend
- Add email/password form to login page
- Add password reset flow
- Keep Google OAuth as alternative
